name: Change Management Cabinet
kind: root
version: 0.1.0
description: Structured change request documentation, risk scoring, and CAB approval routing for IT and DevOps teams. A QA reviewer agent validates every change packet for completeness and risk before a workflow agent routes it to the right approvers and schedules CAB review. Keep ServiceNow as your ITSM system of record; replace the inconsistent change forms, the forgotten rollback plans, and the CAB scheduling chaos around them.
